column5: the home: A funky old renovated house, multiple levels, hardwood and carpeted, surrounded by huge oaks. Access to kitchen and washer and dryer, wifi, 3 living spaces, tv with cable, parking in front or back. Upstairs available to you, lots of room.   Right off freeway, 10 minutes walk to lovely trinity trails and parks, 10 min drive to TCU, bars and restaurants. 15 min drive to downtown Fort Worth. Gorgeous backyard to relax in :)
